        <mxCell id="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-31" parent="1" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;html=1;fontSize=60;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle;align=center;autosizeText=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 32px;&quot;&gt;업로드 RFP 적합성 검사&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="360" x="4189" y="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-32" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fillColor=#f5f5f5;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#666666;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;업로드 RFP 적합성 검사 세부 설명&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. 업로드(transient, 예정) : 사용자가 임의 문서 업로드(&#39;routers/upload&#39;). 영속 저장하지 않음.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. 파싱·임베딩 : 업로드 문서를 파싱 후 &#39;bge-m3&#39;로 임베딩.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. 참조 비교(retrieval) : 참조 코퍼스에서 유사 RFP 청크를 검색(read-only)해 비교 근거 확보.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. 적합성 판정(llm) : 참조 근거를 바탕으로 LLM이 &#39;RFP 적합성&#39;을 판정(누락 항목 및 형식 등 피드백 포함 가능).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5. 결과 반환 : 적합성 결과만 응답. 업로드 문서와 중간 산출물은 DB에 남기지 않음.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="399" width="1080" x="3840" y="561" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-36" edge="1" parent="1" source="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-33" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-35" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-33" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;" value="llm&lt;div&gt;RFP 적합성 판정&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="4725" y="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Pl3Dvy8jhjicuIfsiaQg-35" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;" value="적합성 결과 반환&lt;div&gt;(DB 미기록)&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="4725" y="403" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
